::Firearm::

Firearm walks up to Windcharger. "Hey. I'm Firearm."

He looks the Maximal over, also realizing it was pitch 
black. "External lights," he says into his wrist, the Cybertronian 
Fire's external lights lighting up the area, making it look almost 
like daytime. "That better?"
